"""
tf_diagram.py — Generate AWS networking architecture diagrams from Terraform code.

Uses the `diagrams` library (https://diagrams.mingrammer.com/) to parse .tf files
and produce a visual diagram of your networking infrastructure.

Usage:
    python3 tf_diagram.py /path/to/terraform/repo
    python3 tf_diagram.py /path/to/terraform/repo --output my_diagram --format svg
    python3 tf_diagram.py /path/to/terraform/repo --show-all  # include non-network resources
"""

